The module correctly implements:
- Inverse relationships between name2codepoint and codepoint2name mappings

- HTML5 entity parsing with longest-match semantics
- Numeric character references with proper Unicode boundary handling
- Windows-1252 compatibility mappings
- Optional semicolon parsing per HTML5 spec
- Proper handling of invalid/out-of-range codepoints
